data.description: Assumable 2.5% loan, freshly painted exterior & interior upgraded 2+bedroom w/office-potential bedroom, 2 bath, single level ''Chaparral model home'' Stucco exterior w/tile roof offers a comfortable open floor plan with 10 ft. ceiling in living room.Primary bath features a new walk-in shower with benches, upgraded walk-in closet with custom shelving & wall safe. Spacious primary bedroom has a beautiful bay window. Gourmet kitchen offers granite counters,  island, Jen Air appliances, Tiffany style ceiling fan in dining area, pull out drawers & huge walk-in pantry. Additional features include an electronic remote thermostat, ring doorbell, retractable front screen door & security door, wired security system, hard wired audio speakers in the ceiling, ceiling fans in every room.
